msgctxt "mn9:24-26.6"
msgid "Katamā panāvuso, jāti, katamo jātisamudayo, katamo jātinirodho, katamā jātinirodhagāminī paṭipadā? "
msgstr "But what is rebirth? What is its origin, its cessation, and the practice that leads to its cessation? "

